'''2017年亚洲公路自行车锦标赛'''是第37届[[亚洲自行车锦标赛|亚洲公路自行车锦标赛]]，于2017年2月25日至3月2日在巴林麦纳麦进行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://accasia.org/sites/default/files/TECHNICAL%20GUIDE_VERSION01162015_V_06.pdf|title=TECHNICAL GUIDE|work=Asian Cycling Confederation|date=2017-11-10|accessdate=2020-10-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930213929/http://accasia.org/sites/default/files/TECHNICAL%20GUIDE_VERSION01162015_V_06.pdf|archivedate=2020-09-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。亚洲自行车联合会于2016年决定自2017年开始自行车亚锦赛公路赛和场地赛分开举办，因此该届比赛是两分项分开后的首届亚洲公路自行车锦标赛<ref>{{cite web|url=http://accasia.org/news/separate-asian-track-and-road-championships-2017-and-organize-2015-asian-road-championships|title=To Separate the Asian Track and Road Championships from 2017 and To Organize the 2015 Asian Road Championships in Thailand at Night Time|work=Asian Cycling Confederation|accessdate=2020-09-30|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190504221253/http://accasia.org/news/separate-asian-track-and-road-championships-2017-and-organize-2015-asian-road-championships|archivedate=2019-05-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://cyclingiq.com/2016/04/13/india-and-bahrain-to-co-host-2017-asian-cycling-championships/ |title=India and Bahrain to co-host 2017 Asian Cycling Championships |date=2016-04-13 |accessdate=2019-05-05 |website=CYCLING iQ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180827044928/https://cyclingiq.com/2016/04/13/india-and-bahrain-to-co-host-2017-asian-cycling-championships/ |archivedate=2018-08-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

